---
title: Tex-Mex Pulled Jackfruit Tacos with Sweetcorn Salsa & Creamy Aioli Slaw
description: Jackfruit marinated with mild chilli and lime – our new favourite (and totally irresistible) veggie alternative to pulled pork. Pair it with our tried-and-true Tex-Mex taco recipe that requires zero-fuss assemblage and appears on the plate in a flash.
